    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>Gagan’s Curry House is a specialty restaurant located in Shinagawa, Tokyo, offering authentic Nepalese cuisine and curry. From richly spiced traditional Nepalese curries to tandoori chicken and momo (Nepalese dumplings), we serve a wide variety of flavorful dishes. We also offer Halal-friendly and vegetarian options, so everyone can enjoy our meals with peace of mind. Come and experience the warm taste of Nepal in a cozy, welcoming atmosphere.</p>
